  18. # duplicated from $(ROOTDIR)/runtime/Makefile

  20. # #8985: the meaning of character range a-z depends on the locale, so force C
  21. #        locale throughout.
  22. export LC_ALL=C
  23. (
  24.   for prim in \
  25.       alloc array compare extern floats gc_ctrl hash intern interp ints io \
  26.       lexing md5 meta memprof obj parsing signals str sys callback weak \
  27.       finalise domain platform fiber memory startup_aux runtime_events sync \
  28.       dynlink backtrace_byt backtrace afl \
  29.       bigarray prng
  30.   do
  31.       sed -n -e 's/^CAMLprim value \([a-z0-9_][a-z0-9_]*\).*/\1/p' \
  32.         "runtime/$prim.c"
  33.   done
  34.   sed -n -e 's/^CAMLprim_int64_[0-9](\([a-z0-9_][a-z0-9_]*\)).*/caml_int64_\1\
  35. caml_int64_\1_native/p' runtime/ints.c
  36. ) | sort | uniq
